Description.SourceString: A small, versatile naval jack of all trades. The “Charon” is fitted with a single mortar cannon and two tripod mounts. Effective at both shoreline assaults and hit and run tactics against larger vessels.
Description.LocalizedString: Designed for river patrols, the Type-C Charon is fitted with twin tripod mounts, and a mortar cannon designed to sunder any armoured resistance on the shore or on open waters.
